{"tid":248918,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【特朗普洩密】Bitcoin三日累升15% 破1900美元創新高","createTime":"2017-05-19T02:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T02:48:52.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d3fc2818b44e3a276f4ecc226a10b9ea39579ac5","tid":248918,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170519/large/1495154947_7d7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170519%2Flarge%2F1495154947_7d7b.jpg&h=79168d91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特朗普洩密事件暫時解除，不過VIX恐慌指數仍企於14點以上，避險資金繼續流入，加上日圓滙價輕微下跌，日圓資金繼續炒高比特幣Bitcoin，由低位1,798美元急彈超過100美元至目前的1,916美元，再創新高。<br />\n<br />\nBitcoin三日前曾跌至1,657低位，3日以來反彈逾15%，分析認為市場持續有不明朗因素，Bitcoin比外滙更能分散風險。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56713296&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170519\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56713296%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170519&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sKMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=5456339f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56713296%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170519&h=b4403071\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56713296&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170519</a>"}]}